            552.3358154296875,
            204.06002807617188
          ],
          "text": "RBI/2019-20/69  \nMaster Direction DCM (CC) No.G-6/03.41.01/2019-20  \n       July 01, 2019 \n(Updated as on January 6, 2020)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            223.37998962402344,
            282.7572937011719,
            271.5000305175781
          ],
          "text": "The Chairman and Managing Director / \nChief Executive Officers, \nAll Banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            285.5400085449219,
            172.71600341796875,
            301.9200134277344
          ],
          "text": "Madam / Dear Sir,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            317.14801025390625,
            552.3400268554688,
            350.23199462890625
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) based on \nperformance in rendering customer service to the members of public",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99998474121094,
            366.0791931152344,
            552.3423461914062,
            461.9399719238281
          ],
          "text": "In terms of the Preamble, under Section 45 of the RBI Act, 1934 and 35 A of the Banking \nRegulation Act, 1949, the Bank issues guidelines / instructions for realising the objectives \nof our Clean Note Policy. With a view to sustaining these objectives, the Bank has \nformulated a scheme of incentives titled Currency Distribution and Exchange Scheme \n(CDES) in order to ensure that all bank branches provide better customer services to \nmembers of public.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            482.15997314453125,
            548.9786987304688,
            514.3800048828125
          ],
          "text": "2. The Master Direction enclosed incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the subject.\nThe Direction will be updated from time to time as and when fresh instructions are issued.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            534.8400268554688,
            467.4960021972656,
            551.2200317382812
          ],
          "text": "3. This Master Direction has been placed on RBI website at www.rbi.org.in.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            577.2000122070312,
            157.416015625,
            593.5800170898438
          ],
          "text": "Yours faithfully,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            634.0800170898438,
            210.0360107421875,
            664.260009765625
          ],
          "text": "(Manas Ranjan Mohanty) \nChief General Manager",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
