      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            12.70800495147705,
            552.3359985351562,
            71.2919692993164
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            77.927978515625,
            552.3399047851562,
            126.8520278930664
          ],
          "text": "Circular on “Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES)” for bank branches \nincluding currency chests based on performance in rendering customer service to \nmembers of public",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            135.468017578125,
            552.3397827148438,
            199.68008422851562
          ],
          "text": "1. The Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) for bank branches including \ncurrency chests has been formulated in order to ensure that all bank branches provide \nbetter customer service to members of public with regard to exchange of notes and coins, \nin keeping with the objectives of Clean Note Policy.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            208.96807861328125,
            150.6959991455078,
            226.15206909179688
          ],
          "text": "2. Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            237.00010681152344,
            552.3410034179688,
            269.2801208496094
          ],
          "text": "As per the scheme, banks are eligible for the following financial incentives for providing \nfacilities for exchange of notes and coins:",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            85.91999816894531,
            281.0880126953125,
            108.57599639892578,
            312.0719909667969
          ],
          "text": "Sr. \nNo.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            163.44000244140625,
            281.0880126953125,
            495.9960021972656,
            298.2720031738281
          ],
          "text": "Nature of Service \nParticulars of Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            320.6400146484375,
            319.18798828125,
            537.9371948242188,
            336.3719787597656
          ],
          "text": "a. Capital Cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            92.22000122070312,
            319.3199768066406,
            304.6584777832031,
            383.3399963378906
          ],
          "text": "i) \nOpening \nof \nand \nmaintaining \ncurrency chests at centers having \npopulation of less than 1 lakh in \nunder banked States",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            320.6400146484375,
            335.219970703125,
            537.9398193359375,
            461.23199462890625
          ],
          "text": "50% of capital expenditure subject \nto a ceiling of ₹ 50 lakh per currency \nchest.  In the North Eastern region \nup to 100% of capital expenditure is \neligible for reimbursement subject to \nthe ceiling of ₹ 50 lakh. \n \nb. Revenue cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b16",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            343.1400146484375,
            460.0799865722656,
            537.9384765625,
            539.9400024414062
          ],
          "text": "50% of revenue expenditure for the \nfirst 3 years. In the North Eastern \nregion 50% of revenue expenditure \nwill be reimbursed for the first 5 \nyears.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            90.9000015258789,
            549.9000244140625,
            303.5784912109375,
            613.9200439453125
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nExchange \nof \nsoiled \nnotes/ \nadjudication \nof \nmutilated \nbanknotes over the counter at \nbank branches",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            335.5199890136719,
            553.968017578125,
            528.7559814453125,
            571.1520385742188
          ],
          "text": "a. Exchange of soiled notes – ₹ 2",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            335.5199890136719,
            573.8400268554688,
            528.7572631835938,
            606.0599975585938
          ],
          "text": "per packet for exchange of soiled \nnotes up to denomination ₹ 50",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            335.5199890136719,
            615.3480224609375,
            528.7559814453125,
            647.8200073242188
          ],
          "text": "b. Adjudication of mutilated notes \n– ₹ 2 per piece",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99429321289062,
            778.0344848632812,
            315.73931884765625,
            806.165283203125
          ],
          "text": "1",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 10.98,
            "name": "Calibri",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            89.58000183105469,
            13.319988250732422,
            543.5797729492188,
            29.759984970092773
          ],
          "text": "iii) \nDistribution of coins over counter i. ₹ 25 per bag for distribution of coins over",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            311.0400085449219,
            29.220012664794922,
            543.5759887695312,
            75.29996490478516
          ],
          "text": "the counter. \n \nii. The incentives would be paid on the",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            327.239990234375,
            74.75999450683594,
            543.5762939453125,
            107.0400161743164
          ],
          "text": "basis of withdrawal from currency chest, \nwithout waiting for claims from banks.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            311.0400085449219,
            124.43998718261719,
            543.5772705078125,
            140.81997680664062
          ],
          "text": "iii. Banks may put in place a system of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            311.0400085449219,
            140.3400115966797,
            543.579833984375,
            218.10000610351562
          ],
          "text": "checks and balances to ensure that \ncoins are distributed to retail customers \nin small lots and not to bulk customers. \n \niv. The distribution of coins shall be verified",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            327.239990234375,
            217.61997985839844,
            543.578369140625,
            281.5799865722656
          ],
          "text": "by \nRBI \nRegional \nOffices \nthrough \ninspection of currency chest / incognito \nvisits to branches etc.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            300.0480041503906,
            477.2760009765625,
            323.2200012207031
          ],
          "text": "3. \nOperational Guidelines to avail performance-based incentives –",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            329.1000061035156,
            552.3436279296875,
            393.05999755859375
          ],
          "text": "i) \nThe incentives will be paid on the soiled notes actually received in the Issue Office \nof the RBI. Banks need not submit a separate claim in this regard. Currency chest branch \nwill have to pass on the incentive to the linked branches for the soiled notes tendered / \ncoins distributed by them on a pro-rata basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00003051757812,
            402.5400085449219,
            552.3409423828125,
            450.6600036621094
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nSimilarly, incentive will be paid in respect of the adjudicated notes received along \nwith the soiled note remittances / sent separately by registered / insured post in a sealed \ncover to the RBI. No separate claim is required to be made.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            236.58004760742188,
            460.1399841308594,
            387.75604248046875,
